","dir":"Reference","previous_headings":"","what":"Arguments","title":"Generate Demo Evidence Data — generate_demo_evidence","text":"n_rows Approximate number evidence rows generate. Default 50. study_id Study identifier. Default \"DEMO-001\".","code":""},{"path":"https://r4sub.github.io/r4subui/reference/generate_demo_evidence.html","id":"value","dir":"Reference","previous_headings":"","what":"Value","title":"Generate Demo Evidence Data — generate_demo_evidence","text":"validated evidence data.frame.","code":""},{"path":"https://r4sub.github.io/r4subui/reference/generate_demo_evidence.html","id":"ref-examples","dir":"Reference","previous_headings":"","what":"Examples","title":"Generate Demo Evidence Data — generate_demo_evidence","text":"","code":"ev <- generate_demo_evidence() #> ℹ Run context created: \"R4S-20260316101257-wl4dieex\" #> ✔ Evidence table created: 50 rows nrow(ev) #> [1] 50"},{"path":"https://r4sub.github.io/r4subui/reference/mod_authority_server.html","id":null,"dir":"Reference","previous_headings":"","what":"Authority Profile Module Server — mod_authority_server","title":"Authority Profile Module Server — mod_authority_server","text":"Authority Profile Module Server","code":""},{"path":"https://r4sub.github.io/r4subui/reference/mod_authority_server.html","id":"ref-usage","dir":"Reference","previous_headings":"","what":"Usage","title":"Authority Profile Module Server — mod_authority_server","text":"","code":"mod_authority_server(id, evidence_rv)"},{"path":"https://r4sub.github.io/r4subui/reference/mod_authority_server.html","id":"arguments","dir":"Reference","previous_headings":"","what":"Arguments","title":"Authority Profile Module Server — mod_authority_server","text":"id Module namespace ID. evidence_rv reactive returning validated evidence data.frame.","code":""},{"path":"https://r4sub.github.io/r4subui/reference/mod_authority_server.html","id":"value","dir":"Reference","previous_headings":"","what":"Value","title":"Authority Profile Module Ser