ace_ui","text":"id Module namespace ID.","code":""},{"path":"https://r4sub.github.io/r4subui/reference/mod_trace_ui.html","id":"value","dir":"Reference","previous_headings":"","what":"Value","title":"Traceability Module UI — mod_trace_ui","text":"Shiny UI element.","code":""},{"path":"https://r4sub.github.io/r4subui/reference/r4sub_app.html","id":null,"dir":"Reference","previous_headings":"","what":"Launch the R4SUB Dashboard — r4sub_app","title":"Launch the R4SUB Dashboard — r4sub_app","text":"Starts interactive Shiny dashboard exploring R4SUB evidence, pillar scores, SCI, sensitivity analysis.","code":""},{"path":"https://r4sub.github.io/r4subui/reference/r4sub_app.html","id":"ref-usage","dir":"Reference","previous_headings":"","what":"Usage","title":"Launch the R4SUB Dashboard — r4sub_app","text":"","code":"r4sub_app(evidence = NULL, theme = r4sub_theme(), ...)"},{"path":"https://r4sub.github.io/r4subui/reference/r4sub_app.html","id":"arguments","dir":"Reference","previous_headings":"","what":"Arguments","title":"Launch the R4SUB Dashboard — r4sub_app","text":"evidence optional pre-loaded evidence data.frame. NULL, app shows upload interface. theme bslib::bs_theme object. Default uses r4sub_theme(). ... Additional arguments passed shiny::shinyApp().","code":""},{"path":"https://r4sub.github.io/r4subui/reference/r4sub_app.html","id":"value","dir":"Reference","previous_headings":"","what":"Value","title":"Launch the R4SUB Dashboard — r4sub_app","text":"Shiny app object (returned invisibly; runs interactively).","code":""},{"path":"https://r4sub.github.io/r4subui/reference/r4sub_app.html","id":"ref-examples","dir":"Reference","previous_headings":"","what":"Examples","title":"Launch the R4SUB Dashboard — r4sub_app","text":"","code":"if (FALSE) { # \\dontrun{ # With pre-loaded evidence r4sub_app(evidence = my_evidence)  # With upload interface r4sub_app() } # }"},{"path":"https://r4sub.github.io/r4subui/reference/r4sub_theme.html","id":null,"dir":"Reference","previous_headings":"","what":"Default R4SUB Dashboard Theme — r4sub_theme","title":"Default R4SUB Dashboard Theme — r4sub_theme","text":"Returns bslib::bs_theme() R4SUB dashboard clean, professional look.","code":""},{"path":"https://r4sub.github.io/r4subui/reference/r4sub_theme.html","id":"ref-usage","dir":"Reference","previous_headings":"","what":"Usage","title":"Default R4SUB Dashboard Theme — r4sub_theme","text":"","code":"r4sub_theme(   primary = \"#2C3E50\",   success = \"#27AE60\",   warning = \"#F39C12\",   danger = \"#E74C3C\",   font_scale = 1 )"},{"path":"https://r4sub.github.io/r4subui/reference/r4sub_theme.html","id":"arguments","dir":"Reference","previous_headings":"","what":"Arguments","title":"Default R4SUB Dashboard Theme — r4sub_theme","text":"primary Primary accent color. Default \"#2C3E50\". success Success/pass color. Default \"#27AE60\". warning Warning color. Default \"#F39C12\". danger Danger/fail color. Default \"#E74C3C\". font_scale Numeric font scale factor. Default 1.","code":""},{"path":"https://r4sub.github.io/r4subui/reference/r4sub_theme.html","id":"value","dir":"Reference","previous_headings":"","what":"Value","title":"Default R4SUB Dashboard Theme — r4sub_theme","text":"bslib::bs_theme object.","code":""},{"path":"https://r4sub.github.io/r4subui/reference/r4sub_theme.html","id":"ref-examples","dir":"Reference","previous_headings":"","what":"Examples","title":"Default R4SUB Dashboard Theme — r4sub_theme","text":"","code":"theme <- r4sub_theme()"},{"path":"https://r4sub.github.io/r4subui/reference/r4sub_value_box.html","id":null,"dir":"Reference","previous_headings":"","what":"Create a Summary Value Box — r4sub_value_box","title":"Create a Summary Value Box — r4sub_value_box","text":"Creates styled value box displaying single metric.","code":""},{"path":"https://r4sub.github.io/r4subui/reference/r4sub_value_box.html","id":"ref-usage","dir":"Reference","previous_headings":"","what":"Usage","title":"Create a Summary Value Box — r4sub_value_box","text":"","code":"r4sub_value_box(title, value, theme = \"primary\", subtitle = NULL)"},{"path":"https://r4sub.github.io/r4subui/reference/r4sub_value_box.html","id":"arguments","dir":"Reference","previous_headings":"","what":"Arguments","title":"Create a Summary Value Box — r4sub_value_box","text":"title Character label. value value display. theme Character theme: \"primary\", \"success\", \"warning\", \"danger\", \"info\". Default \"primary\". subtitle Optional subtitle text.","code":""},{"path":"https://r4sub.github.io/r4subui/reference/r4sub_value_box.html","id":"value","dir":"Reference","previous_headings":"","what":"Value","title":"Create a Summary Value Box — r4sub_value_box","text":"bslib::value_box element.","code":""},{"path":"https://r4sub.github.io/r4subui/reference/r4sub_value_box.html","id":"ref-examples","dir":"Reference","previous_headings":"","what":"Examples","title":"Create a Summary Value Box — r4sub_value_box","text":"","code":"if (FALSE) { # \\dontrun{ r4sub_value_box(\"SCI Score\", 85.2, theme = \"success\") } # }"},{"path":"https://r4sub.github.io/r4subui/reference/r4subui-package.html","id":null,"dir":"Reference","previous_headings":"","what":"r4subui: Interactive Dashboard for Clinical Submission Readiness — r4subui-package","title":"r4subui: Interactive Dashboard for Clinical Submission Readiness — r4subui-package","text":"Provides interactive Shiny dashboard R4SUB (R Regulatory Submission) ecosystem. Visualizes evidence tables, pillar scores, Submission Confidence Index (SCI), risk registers, traceability coverage, trend analysis. Supports upload evidence data direct integration 'r4subcore', 'r4subtrace', 'r4subrisk', 'r4subscore'.","code":""},{"path":[]},{"path":"https://r4sub.github.io/r4subui/reference/r4subui-package.html","id":"author","dir":"Reference","previous_headings":"","what":"Author","title":"r4subui: Interactive Dashboard for Clinical Submission Readiness — r4subui-package","text":"Maintainer: Pawan Rama Mali prm@outlook.(ORCID) [copyright holder]","code":""},{"path":"https://r4sub.github.io/r4subui/reference/render_evidence_table.html","id":null,"dir":"Reference","previous_headings":"","what":"Render an Evidence Table as HTML — render_evidence_table","title":"Render an Evidence Table as HTML — render_evidence_table","text":"Creates formatted HTML table evidence data.frame, suitable display Shiny app static report.","code":""},{"path":"https://r4sub.github.io/r4subui/reference/render_evidence_table.html","id":"ref-usage","dir":"Reference","previous_headings":"","what":"Usage","title":"Render an Evidence Table as HTML — render_evidence_table","text":"","code":"render_evidence_table(   evidence,   columns = c(\"indicator_id\", \"indicator_domain\", \"severity\", \"result\", \"message\",     \"location\", \"metric_value\"),   max_rows = 500L )"},{"path":"https://r4sub.github.io/r4subui/reference/render_evidence_table.html","id":"arguments","dir":"Reference","previous_headings":"","what":"Arguments","title":"Render an Evidence Table as HTML — render_evidence_table","text":"evidence validated evidence data.frame. columns Character vector column names display. Default shows key columns. max_rows Maximum number rows display. Default 500.","code":""},{"path":"https://r4sub.github.io/r4subui/reference/render_evidence_table.html","id":"value","dir":"Reference","previous_headings":"","what":"Value","title":"Render an Evidence Table as HTML — render_evidence_table","text":"HTML tags object (shiny::tags$table).","code":""},{"path":"https://r4sub.github.io/r4subui/reference/render_evidence_table.html","id":"ref-examples","dir":"Reference","previous_headings":"","what":"Examples","title":"Render an Evidence Table as HTML — render_evidence_table","text":"","code":"if (FALSE) { # \\dontrun{ render_evidence_table(evidence) } # }"}]
